title: Waiver-Wire Adds, Predicting Breakouts, and Deceiving Yards | The Dantasy Football Podcast
description:
Danny Kelly, Danny Heifetz, and Craig Horlbeck highlight the biggest fantasy football story lines of the week, debate the most important waiver-wire adds, and break down key usage trends from Week 1.
